title: Telegraph Ave
lyrics:
On November 21st, 2018, Billie Eilish and Finneas O'Connell performed a brief acoustic cover of Childish Gambino’s “Telegraph Ave” for SiriusXM.
I don't really want to drive
But I think I'd rather die
In Oakland, in Oakland
With my hands on two and ten
So I guess it all depends
On Oakland, on Oakland
And I'm nervous, truth be told
I never saw me growing old
In Oakland, in Oakland
And if I married you tonight
It would probably start a riot
In Oakland, in Oakland
Foot on the gas
I'm just tryna pass
All the red lights
And the stop signs
I'm ready to go
